Modifications by this fork
--------------------------
Maintainer: tomoya0318 <noguchitomoya0318@gmail.com>

Summary of changes relative to upstream:

- Removed the runtime dependency on the `anthropic` Python SDK so the
  skill no longer requires an `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`.
- Rewired `scripts/improve_description.py` to call `claude -p --effort <level>`
  via subprocess, reusing the same Claude subscription auth that powers
  Claude Code itself.
- Updated `scripts/run_loop.py` to drop the SDK client initialization and
  consume the new subprocess-based description improver.
- Added/updated SKILL.md with a fork notice and pointer to this NOTICE.

